        <h1>Flowers API</h1>
        <p>Flowers API scrapes its data from <a class="link" target="_blank"
                href="https://www.proflowers.com/blog/types-of-flowers/">ProFlowers</a>, this API has been created by <a
                class="link" target="_blank" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/ahmed0saber/">ahmed0saber</a>, click the
