        <a class="btn" href="/projects">View Projects</a>
    </main>
    <span class="separator"></span>
    <section>
        <h2>Usage</h2>
        <p>To get data of all flowers, send a <span>GET</span> request to <span>/all</span> endpoint.</p>
        <p>To get data of a certain flower, send a <span>GET</span> request to <span>/flower/1</span> endpoint, as 1 is
            the index of flower.</p>
        <p>To get data of certain number of flowers, send a <span>GET</span> request to <span>/flowers/1,5,7</span>
            endpoint, as 1, 5 and 7 are indexes of these flowers.</p>
    </section>
